data.description: NEWLY RELISTED after minor cosmetic updates ...Move-in ready enjoy the holidays in your new home, you can start making memories from day one.…  4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths,2080 sqft  Large Kitchen & spacious Backyard with deck for relaxing and or entertaining! Tucked away in the most charming corner of Dekalb County near Ponce De Leon and 7 min from N Druid Hills, this charming home is complete with a BRAND NEW ROOF as well as a NEW garage, New Carpet, New fixtures, New Paint and New kitchen cabinets…to make life just that much sweeter! Meet your neighbors, your soon-to-be lifelong friends, as you step into a world where community thrives and everyone says "hello how are you" like they mean it. Ready for just a small amount of your own special touches to make this home just what you want it to be …waiting for you to move in and start the next chapter of your incredible story.      28 mins to Hartsfield- Jackson International airport 11 min to Dekalb Farmers Market  near all shopping    Don't miss out on this opportunity to make 1111 Bramwell Lane your dream home. Schedule a showing today!"
